name: slamby-insight
description: Cross-platform (electron based) integrated data management tool, dedicated for data-scientists and managers. Quick real-time data access, data-analysis and data-processing.

scripts.packager:prepare: npm run build && node tasks/prepare-packager.js && cd packager/temp && npm i
scripts.packager:win32: npm run packager:win32:x86 && npm run packager:win32:x64
scripts.packager:linux: npm run packager:linux:x86 && npm run packager:linux:x64
scripts.packager: npm run packager:win32 && npm run packager:linux && npm run packager:osx
scripts.installer:debian: npm run installer:debian:x86 && npm run installer:debian:x64
scripts.installer:redhat: npm run installer:redhat:x86 && npm run installer:redhat:x64
scripts.installer: npm run installer:win && npm run installer:debian
